vices, such as solar cells, where an increase in\ntemperature has drastic effects on performance. Our 2D thermo-functional\nmaterial includes a single layer of spheres emitting long-wave radiation\nthrough the infrared atmospheric window and over a broad wavelength ange, thus\nproviding effective radiative cooling using the outer space as a heat sink at 3\nK.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 23 Oct 2019 14:50:56 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 30 Oct 2019 15:47:16 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-10-31"}
